# BancoPro Case Study: Credit Process Transformation

## Before TechFlow
![Manual banking process](assets/banco-before.png)
- **Average time:** 5 days per application
- **Manual documents:** 47 different forms
- **Error rate:** 12% in manual review
- **Dedicated staff:** 85 analysts
- **Cost per application:** $150

## After TechFlow
![Automated process](assets/banco-after.png)
- **Average time:** 2 automated hours
- **Digital documents:** Automatic OCR capture
- **Error rate:** 0.8% with AI validation
- **Dedicated staff:** 12 supervisors
- **Cost per application:** $18

