# LogiCorp Case Study: Supply Chain Automation

## 1. 📦 Order Receipt
Automatic integration with e-commerce, ERP, and POS systems

## 2. 🎯 Route Optimization
AI calculates optimal routes considering traffic, weather, and capacity

## 3. 🚚 Automatic Assignment
Smart distribution to carriers based on location and availability

## 4. 📱 Real-Time Tracking
Automatic updates to customers with precise ETAs

## 5. 📊 Predictive Analytics
Machine learning continuously improves route efficiency

## 6. 💰 Automatic Billing
Automatic generation and delivery of post-delivery invoices

